A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Vehicle Laws – Electric Bicycles – Certificate of Title, Registration, and
3 Insurance
4 FOR the purpose of requiring an electric bicycle to be titled and registered by the Motor
5 Vehicle Administration; requiring an application for a certificate of title and
6 registration for an electric bicycle to be submitted electronically; requiring an owner
7 of an electric bicycle to maintain certain security; authorizing an insurer to exclude
8 certain benefits from a policy for electric bicycles; and generally relating to the titling
9 and registration of, and insurance for, electric bicycles.
